		"description": "<p><em>Wondrous item</em></p><p>This viscous, milky-white substance can form a permanent adhesive bond between any two objects. It must be stored in a jar or flask that has been coated inside with oil of slipperiness. When found, a container contains 1d6 + 1 ounces.</p><p>One ounce of the glue can cover a 1-foot square surface. The glue takes 1 minute to set. Once it has done so, the bond it creates can be broken only by the application of universal solvent or oil of etherealness, or with a @Compendium[dnd5e.spells.3okM6Gn63zzEULkz]{Wish} spell.</p><section class=\"secret foundry-note\" id=\"secret-s3MCPshCsEZEYTHn\"><p><strong>Foundry Note</strong></p><p>The 7 charges reflect the maximum amount a character can find. Please adjust as required.</p></section>",
